# CDK specific
cdk.out/
# cdk.context.json is intentionally NOT ignored — it must be committed.
# CDK writes cached AZ/AMI/SSM lookups there; missing it means the next
# synth may pick different values and produce a surprise diff in CI.
# Optional output files written by `cdk deploy --outputs-file` (CfnOutput
# values for the deployed stacks). Local-only by convention.
cdk-outputs*.json

